changelog.release_notes:
* Experimental support for Pebble 2 and Pebble Time 2;
* Increased network timeout from 10 to 30 seconds;
* Automatically show tasklist if it is the only tasklist available (thanks to Dru for the idea);
* Renamed app to avoid breaking copyrights.

